Program: Outlook
Title: Migration in the Modern World
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrj6
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look at migration, interviews with writer Aleksandar Hemon an involuntary migrant from Sarajevo, now living in the USA, Robin Cohen, editor of Cambridge Survey of World Migration and Jean-Philippe Chauzy of International Organization for Migration. Also, Shaolin monks explain Kung Fu with a theatre show. Finally, a visit to Rapa Nui (Easter Island). Show less